                                    <desc type="GuestText"><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3108RepCh388">Yǝweddǝsǝwwa malāʾǝkt la-Māryām</title>. The name of the
                                        scribe, <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS13086Zarufael">Zarufāʾel</persName>, is mentioned on <locus target="#194r"/>.</desc>
                                    <q xml:lang="gez"><seg part="I">ይዌድስዋ፡ መላእክት፡ ለማርያም፡</seg></q>
                                 </item>
                                
                                <item xml:id="a2" corresp="#h3">
                                    <locus from="194r"/>
                                    <desc type="GuestText"><title type="incomplete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2444Temher">Tǝmhǝrta ḫǝbuʾāt</title></desc>
                                    <q xml:lang="gez"><seg part="I">በእንተ፡ ትምህርተ፡ ህቡዓት፡ ቅድመ፡ ዘትትነገር፡ <sic resp="PRS10171Wright">እምርስፎራ፡</sic> ለምእመናን፡ ህቡዓት፡</seg></q>
                                </item>
                                
                                <item xml:id="a3">
                                    <locus target="#3r"/>
                                    <desc type="OwnershipNote">The note states that the manuscript belongs to the church of 
                                        <placeName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/INS0101MadhaneAlam">Madḫāne ʿĀlam</placeName>.</desc>
                                    <q xml:lang="gez">ዳዊት፡ ማርያም፡ ዘ<placeName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/INS0101MadhaneAlam">ቅዱስ፡ መድኃኔ፡ ዓለም።</placeName>
                                    </q>
                                </item>
                                
                                <item xml:id="e1">
                                    <locus target="#194r"/>
                                    <desc>The name of <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS13088AsmaG">ʾAṣma Giyorgis</persName>, partially erased,
                                        is mentioned on <locus target="#194r"/>,
                                        below that of <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS13086Zarufael">Zarufāʾel</persName>.</desc>
                                </item>
                            </list>
                            
                        </additions>
